Interface ILinkedList<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements in this list
All Known Implementing Classes:
DLL
public interface ILinkedList<E>
Interface for a generic List data structure. Defines common operations for lists, such as adding, getting, setting, and removing elements. The DLLNode<E> add(E element) method is specific to an implementation that returns the node.
